Increased cardiovascular and renal disease but not reduced life expectancy among 
diabetic participants in the general Northern Greek population.

Papanas N(1), Trypsianis G, Tiaka EK, Manolakis AC, Katsavaki D, Birka S, 
Natsiopoulos K, Maltezos E, Papazoglou N.

Author information:
(1)Outpatient Clinic of Obesity, Diabetes and Metabolism, Second Department of 
