[Burden of disease in schistosomiasis japonica. I. Calculation and evaluation of 
years lived with disability of chronic schistosomiasis].

[Article in Chinese]

Jia TW(1), Sun LP, Hong QB, Deng Y, Zhang GH, Wang H, Yi P, Guo JG, Zhou XN.

Author information:
(1)National Institute of Parasitic Diseases, Chinese Center for Disease Control 
